heir relationship to the writing of history.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn English.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 26. Mrz 2024) 0aBloodvFolklore. 0aFolklorezAfrica, Central. 0aFolklorezAfrica, East. 0aVampireszAfrica, Central. 0aVampireszAfrica, East. 7aSOCIAL SCIENCE / Anthropology / Cultural & Social.2bisacsh40uhttps://doi.org/10.1525/9780520922297?locatt=mode:legacy40uhttps://www.degruyter.com/isbn/9780520922297423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/document/cover/isbn/9780520922297/original  aEBA_EMB  aEBA_UCA_YUP  aGBV-deGruyter-alles